name: Laborer Management System
description: A Laborer Management System in PHP helps manage worker records, attendance, wages, and job assignments efficiently. It streamlines labor tracking, payment processing, and performance monitoring for improved workforce management.

name: EyeCare appoinment System
description: An EyeCare Appointment System in PHP allows patients to book, manage, and track eye checkup appointments online. It streamlines scheduling for clinics, reducing wait times and improving patient care.

name: Plant Selling Website
description: A Plant Selling Website in PHP allows users to browse, purchase, and manage plant orders online. It includes features like product listings, a shopping cart, secure checkout, and an admin panel for inventory management.
